    "steam_appid": 3311950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311950/extras/00ca2e034523b0f5afb994956758457f.avif?t=1733875964\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311950/extras_big/00ca2e034523b0f5afb994956758457f.avif?t=1733875964 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >思考更快，行动更快。国际象棋从未如此激动人心，而两步将杀解谜包将你置于行动的核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 准备好将你的战术水平提升到新的高度了吗？两步将杀解谜包提供30个手工制作的谜题，旨在磨练你的直觉并测试你的速度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311950/extras/5e3f751b87a139cc47c4c8343ca124f1.avif?t=1733875964\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311950/extras_big/5e3f751b87a139cc47c4c8343ca124f1.avif?t=1733875964 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是在攀登Elo排名还是在打磨你的棋艺，这些谜题将挑战你在仅仅两步之内找到将杀—完美地培养你致命的直觉。</p>",
